PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the KAWACATOOSE FIRST NATION, of some 959.309 hectares of surface lands and 962.869 hectares of mines and minerals, located in the Rural Municipality of Mount Hope No. 279 and Big Quill No. 308 approximately 26 kilometres north from the town of Raymore, Saskatchewan, as an addition to Kawacatoose Reserve No. 88, Saskatchewan.
